title: Porto Alegre 2015 nº 032 - CONTRASTES!
text:
Only registered TrekEarth members may write critiques. Photographer's Note 
Série sobre o meu passeio a PORTO ALEGRE, a CAPITAL do ESTADO do RIO GRANDE DO SUL, o Estado mais Austral do Brasil - de 16 a 18 de Janeiro de 2015 - nº 032 ! Series on my short trip to PORTO ALEGRE (JOYFUL HARBOR), the CAPITAL CITY of the STATE of RIO GRANDE DO SUL (SOUTHERN BIG RIVER), the most Austral State in Brazil - from January, 16th to 18th, 2015 - #032 ! DETALHES ARQUITETÔNICOS CONTRASTANTES DO CENTRO! DOWNTOWN CONTRASTING ARCHITECTURAL DETAILS! PORTO ALEGRE surprised me and amazed me for the architectural beauties, specially those of buildings built in the last two centuries!
